Adjust base figure to account for statistical disparities, capacity, research, DBE, availability, and other
Develop rational Goal and determine how much DBE participation can be reached using race-neutral measures
Incorporate stakeholder input to methodology and adjust Goal (weighted)
Upload Triennial DBE Goal Report and FTA concurrence to CRBRC shared drive and send to DTR
Publish Trienniel DBE Goal for public comment (30 days or more)
